Title: Butterfly Effects
Description:
We were overwhelmed by her companions. Moraidormi was still killed.

I need another strategy, one that will actually protect her. She is what matters. Go rewind time, including our actions.

After the rewind, I will hold time in place. Then we can try to make defenses for her.
ObjectivesText: After rewinding time, create defenses for Moraidormi and test them.

Objectives.Text: Quickened Sand collected from Timeline Fractures
